and the Decree. We are moving out â€” now.

00:02:14.110 --> 00:02:16.110
Squadron!

00:02:24.869 --> 00:02:29.771
Alyosha, take command.
I'm through with fighting.

00:02:32.263 --> 00:02:34.807
Your sword.

00:02:42.656 --> 00:02:44.137
Where is Napoleon?

00:02:53.905 --> 00:02:57.156
Here you go, Samoilov.
The hell you caught Napoleon.

